description:
In a week that's seen the creative disaster of Rebel Moon Part 2, and the commercial disaster of Ministry of Ungentlemanly Warfare, we ask if Deadpool 3 might be one of the few movies to actually make money this year. Join me, MauLer, Disparu, The Movie Cynic and Echo Chamberlain at the Bar! 

Subscribe to Disparu: https://www.youtube.com/@disparutoo
Subscribe to Movie Cynic: https://www.youtube.com/@TheMovieCynic
Subscribe to Echo: https://www.youtube.com/@EchoChamberlain
title: Open Bar #92 - Rebel Moon 2, Ministry Of Ungentlemanly Warfare, Deadpool 3 Saves Marvel??
